      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 59 judgment</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 59 judgment</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>渙，亨。王假有廟，利涉大川，利貞。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Huan intimates that (under its conditions) there will be progress and success. The king goes to his ancestral temple; and it will be advantageous to cross the great stream. It will be advantageous to be firm and correct.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
