      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 59 初六</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 59 初六</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>初六：用拯馬壯，吉。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The first SIX, divided, shows its subject engaged in rescuing (from the impending evil) and having (the assistance of) a strong horse. There will be good fortune.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
