      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">易經 59 九二</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 59 九二</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九二：渙奔其机，悔亡。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The second NINE, undivided, shows its subject, amid the dispersion, hurrying to his contrivance (for security). All occasion for repentance will disappear.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
