      <prop type="x-translation-ref">易經 59 九五</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>九五：渙汗其大號，渙王居，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The fifth NINE, undivided, shows its subject amidst the dispersion issuing his great announcements as the perspiration (flows from his body). He scatters abroad (also) the accumulations in the royal granaries. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
