      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>上九：渙其血，去逖出，无咎。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The topmost NINE, undivided, shows its subject disposing of (what may be called) its bloody wounds, and going and separating himself from its anxious fears. There will be no error.</seg>
      </tuv>
